+// libstdc++/23871
+
+#include <iostream>
+
+class mytest {
+public:
+  mytest (int);
+  unsigned char operator|| (const mytest&) const;
+  friend unsigned char operator|| (const int&, const mytest&);
+};
+
+inline unsigned char operator|| (const int& lhs, const mytest& rhs)
+{
+  std::cout << 1 << std::endl;
+  return (mytest)lhs || rhs;
+}
